result.name: calderdale-financial-information
result.notes:
All invoices of £500 and over (inc. VAT).
Amount paid shown net of VAT.
This is the actual cost to the Council.

All information is drawn from payment feeders into the Council's financial ledger.
Details of all expenditure apart from benefit payments and employee pay have been published.
Where there is any specific sensitive information, this has been redacted
(i.e the individual payments are still listed but no personal details have been disclosed).
Redaction applies to social service payments to adult and foster carers.
